001package com.pingidentity.sdk.pingonewallet.types;
002
003import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
004
005import com.pingidentity.did.sdk.types.Request;
006
007import java.io.IOException;
008import java.util.List;
009import java.util.Map;
010import java.util.stream.Collectors;
011
012@SuppressWarnings("unused")
013public class CredentialRequest {
014
015    private final String createdAt;
016    private final String applicationInstanceId;
017    private final String sessionId;
018    private final String message;
019    private final String action;
020    private final List<String> requestedKeys;
021
022    public static CredentialRequest fromRequest(@NonNull final Request request) throws IOException {
023        return new CredentialRequest(request.getDetails());
024    }
025
026    @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")
027    public CredentialRequest(Map<String, Object> details) throws IOException {
028        final Map<String, Object> map = (Map<String, Object>) details.getOrDefault("shocard", null);
029        if (map == null || map.isEmpty() || !map.containsKey("shocardid") || !map.containsKey("ss_id")) {
030            throw new IOException("Missing required info in map");
031        }
032        this.createdAt = (String) map.get("created_at");
033        this.applicationInstanceId = (String) map.get("shocardid");
034        this.sessionId = (String) map.get("ss_id");
035        this.message = (String) map.get("message");
036        this.action = (String) map.get("action");
037        this.requestedKeys = (List<String>) map.get("requested_keys");
038    }
039
040    public CredentialRequest(String createdAt, String applicationInstanceId, String sessionId, String message, String action, List<String> requestedKeys) {
041        this.createdAt = createdAt;
042        this.applicationInstanceId = applicationInstanceId;
043        this.sessionId = sessionId;
044        this.message = message;
045        this.action = action;
046        this.requestedKeys = requestedKeys;
047    }
048
049    public String getCreatedAt() {
050        return createdAt;
051    }
052
053    public String getApplicationInstanceId() {
054        return applicationInstanceId;
055    }
056
057    public String getSessionId() {
058        return sessionId;
059    }
060
061    public String getMessage() {
062        return message;
063    }
064
065    public String getAction() {
066        return action;
067    }
068
069    public List<String> getStringRequestedKeys() {
070        return requestedKeys;
071    }
072
073    public List<RequestedKey> getRequestedKeys() {
074        return requestedKeys.stream()
075                .map(RequestedKey::new)
076                .collect(Collectors.toList());
077    }
078}
